OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBreezy
OL,6,Ftonight with clear spells and
OL,7,Foccasional showers moving through.
OL,8,FThese could be heavy at times before
OL,9,Feasing by dawn. Staying mild overnight
OL,10,Fwith the brisk winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA largely dry start with
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Turning cloudier into
OL,14,Fthe afternoon with a few showers
OL,15,Fpossible, followed by more persistent
OL,16,Frain arriving later. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
